1) Install react js and Tailwind css
- npm create vite@latest --> folder name "client" --> React --> JavaScript + SWC
- cd client --> npm install --> Now you can run the app

2) Search Tailwind css installation steps from --> https://tailwindcss.com/docs/guides/vite
- Install --> npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
- Initialize --> npx tailwindcss init -p
- Open tailwind.config.js  and change all the file in it with the new file from the tailwind website.
- Copy and paste the three lines of code form index.css (from the website) to the client file folder index.css
  src --> index.css --> 
                      @tailwind base;
                      @tailwind components;
                      @tailwind utilities;
- 